&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://5itomato.github.io/p/minecraft-tutorial/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1928&#34;
	height=&#34;1152&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://5itomato.github.io/p/minecraft-tutorial/2_hu3389699993495350210.png 480w, https://5itomato.github.io/p/minecraft-tutorial/2_hu958659855944736502.png 1024w&#34;
